{
  "stem": "10859.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I worked over there very hard.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And the fact is while I was working at that job, I could support my family, too.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Because I had a lot of connections with food in the restaurant.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "My brother used to come once in a while.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I used to help him out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I was with them from 1939 till 1941, with the Russians.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "That's where they were there, two years, in Luck.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I will still not forget as long as I live the party that our restaurant had to make for officials from Russia.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "At that time, his name was Khrushchev.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Khrushchev was later the leader of the Russian government.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But he was at that time the secretary of the party of Ukraine.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And his place was Kiev.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Probably you have heard Kiev.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "It's a big city, one of the big cities in Russia.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And that Khrushchev came with a bunch of generals to us to have a conference, a meeting, with the Russians.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And that conference and that meeting was in my restaurant, where I was-- restaurant, [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH].",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "They called it [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "It means, like, German, something like that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "The [NON-ENGLISH], which is like here the FBI.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "To understand what it means, the [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH] is like the FBI.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "They came a day before, investigate me and talked with me, make sure that everything will be all right.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Because a big man like Khrushchev is coming.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "He's going to eat in the restaurant.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And there was a big evening, music.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "There was dancing and everything and speeches.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And they drink the toast to one another.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH SPEECH].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "That means, live, stallion, and Hitler.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "Because they were buddies at the time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "They were friend.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "Of course, he later attacked them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And they didn't even know.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
